03:20:08.060 --> 03:20:08.340
you know

03:20:08.340 --> 03:20:09.480
in greek

03:20:09.480 --> 03:20:10.020
means

03:20:10.020 --> 03:20:12.140
that which sets

03:20:12.140 --> 03:20:13.140
uh

03:20:13.140 --> 03:20:15.260
things into a state of contradiction

03:20:15.260 --> 03:20:16.280
or dynamic

03:20:16.280 --> 03:20:16.980
tension

03:20:16.980 --> 03:20:18.300
so

03:20:18.300 --> 03:20:19.020
um

03:20:19.020 --> 03:20:20.360
the diabolical

03:20:20.360 --> 03:20:21.700
in its

03:20:21.700 --> 03:20:22.900
terms of its greek root

03:20:22.900 --> 03:20:23.700
diabolane

03:20:23.700 --> 03:20:24.880
means

03:20:24.880 --> 03:20:25.420
uh

03:20:25.420 --> 03:20:28.000
setting into a state of dynamic opposition

03:20:28.000 --> 03:20:29.560
dynamic tension

03:20:29.560 --> 03:20:32.380
in a way that causes growth

03:20:32.380 --> 03:20:33.000
there you go

03:20:33.000 --> 03:20:35.080
so to look back at the hegelian dialectic

03:20:35.080 --> 03:20:36.400
which we discussed a little bit in our

03:20:36.400 --> 03:20:37.280
first conversation

03:20:37.280 --> 03:20:38.060
you know hegel

03:20:38.060 --> 03:20:38.720
thought that

03:20:38.720 --> 03:20:40.400
thesis and antithesis

03:20:40.400 --> 03:20:42.160
at all levels in society

03:20:42.160 --> 03:20:44.840
from the psychological to the political

03:20:44.840 --> 03:20:46.040
uh

03:20:46.040 --> 03:20:46.700
the the

03:20:46.700 --> 03:20:49.600
opposition of a thesis and an antithesis

03:20:49.600 --> 03:20:50.840
created the

03:20:50.840 --> 03:20:51.920
dialectical

03:20:51.920 --> 03:20:53.960
synthetic motor of history

03:20:53.960 --> 03:20:54.880
moving forward

03:20:54.880 --> 03:20:55.460
right

03:20:55.460 --> 03:20:56.060
and that all

03:20:56.060 --> 03:20:56.880
novel

03:20:56.880 --> 03:20:57.760
uh

03:20:57.760 --> 03:20:58.240
structures

03:20:58.240 --> 03:20:59.480
emerge from out of this kind of

03:20:59.480 --> 03:21:00.380
dialectical opposition

03:21:00.380 --> 03:21:02.580
and

03:21:02.580 --> 03:21:03.720
also

03:21:03.720 --> 03:21:05.800
setting into a state of dynamic tension

03:21:05.800 --> 03:21:09.260
can mean creating conundrums

03:21:09.260 --> 03:21:10.300
puzzles

03:21:10.300 --> 03:21:13.380
seeming absurdities

03:21:13.380 --> 03:21:15.120
that force the mind

03:21:15.120 --> 03:21:16.820
to the limit of its capacities

03:21:16.820 --> 03:21:19.360
and that ultimately demand

03:21:19.360 --> 03:21:20.460
a

03:21:20.460 --> 03:21:22.080
growth of human cognitive

03:21:22.080 --> 03:21:23.360
faculties

03:21:23.360 --> 03:21:24.820
you see

03:21:24.820 --> 03:21:25.800
because

03:21:25.800 --> 03:21:28.300
if you're grappling

03:21:28.300 --> 03:21:29.180
with a problem

03:21:29.180 --> 03:21:30.600
that has no solution

03:21:30.600 --> 03:21:32.820
because it's deliberately absurd

03:21:32.820 --> 03:21:36.060
you may figure out all kinds of other things along the way

03:21:36.060 --> 03:21:37.680
you might not solve

03:21:37.680 --> 03:21:38.760
solve the problem

03:21:38.760 --> 03:21:40.960
but it will engage your cognitive

03:21:40.960 --> 03:21:42.760
and aesthetic faculties

03:21:42.760 --> 03:21:46.380
in a way that's liable to lead to an increase of capacity

03:21:46.380 --> 03:21:48.140
a refinement of perception

03:21:48.140 --> 03:21:49.160
and

03:21:49.160 --> 03:21:50.740
an expansion of imagination

03:21:50.740 --> 03:21:52.140
of creative imagination

03:21:52.140 --> 03:21:55.600
so if you look through folklore

03:21:55.600 --> 03:21:56.580
as Kalawa argued

03:21:56.580 --> 03:21:58.580
the mantis has been associated with this apparently

03:21:58.580 --> 03:21:59.740
hmm

03:21:59.740 --> 03:22:02.280
so I found that very interesting

03:22:02.280 --> 03:22:04.080
I also put that

03:22:04.080 --> 03:22:05.060
in closer encounters

03:22:05.060 --> 03:22:06.620
next to cases

03:22:06.620 --> 03:22:07.680
where people say

03:22:07.680 --> 03:22:08.380
they saw

03:22:08.380 --> 03:22:09.360
um

03:22:09.360 --> 03:22:11.080
greys turn into owls

03:22:11.080 --> 03:22:12.700
and they saw

03:22:12.700 --> 03:22:14.960
what they believed were owls

03:22:14.960 --> 03:22:15.980
turn into greys

03:22:15.980 --> 03:22:17.160
when their screen memories

03:22:17.160 --> 03:22:18.340
were subjected to

03:22:18.340 --> 03:22:19.780
analysis under

03:22:19.780 --> 03:22:20.800
regression hypnosis

03:22:20.800 --> 03:22:23.520
there's a whole plethora of cases

03:22:23.520 --> 03:22:24.160
I'm forgetting

03:22:24.160 --> 03:22:24.920
it's a name

03:22:24.920 --> 03:22:26.240
maybe Mike Cleland

03:22:26.240 --> 03:22:27.020
a guy who wrote

03:22:27.020 --> 03:22:27.760
a whole study

03:22:27.760 --> 03:22:28.600
two books on this

03:22:28.600 --> 03:22:29.780
on owls

03:22:29.780 --> 03:22:30.980
in the close encounter phenomena

03:22:30.980 --> 03:22:31.400
hmm

03:22:31.400 --> 03:22:32.900
and David Lynch

03:22:32.900 --> 03:22:33.820
clearly knew about this

03:22:33.820 --> 03:22:34.940
because if you watch Twin Peaks

03:22:34.940 --> 03:22:35.220
you know

03:22:35.220 --> 03:22:35.760
one of the

03:22:35.760 --> 03:22:36.980
most important

03:22:36.980 --> 03:22:38.360
koans

03:22:38.360 --> 03:22:39.300
zen koans

03:22:39.300 --> 03:22:40.060
in Twin Peaks

03:22:40.060 --> 03:22:40.820
is the owls

03:22:40.820 --> 03:22:41.720
are not what they seem

03:22:41.720 --> 03:22:42.000
hmm

03:22:42.000 --> 03:22:43.120
radically surrealist

03:22:43.120 --> 03:22:43.400
mm-hmm

03:22:43.400 --> 03:22:44.380
David Lynch is a

03:22:44.380 --> 03:22:46.240
modern American surrealist

03:22:46.240 --> 03:22:46.400
hmm

03:22:46.400 --> 03:22:48.060
and if you

03:22:48.060 --> 03:22:49.560
so there's a lot of

03:22:49.560 --> 03:22:51.100
engagement with

03:22:51.100 --> 03:22:51.880
shamanism

03:22:51.880 --> 03:22:52.880
in surrealism

03:22:52.880 --> 03:22:54.500
uh

03:22:54.500 --> 03:22:55.640
that involves

03:22:55.640 --> 03:22:56.280
the symbolism

03:22:56.280 --> 03:22:57.400
of the praying mantis

03:22:57.400 --> 03:22:59.120
and symbolism of owls

03:22:59.120 --> 03:22:59.920
mm-hmm

03:22:59.920 --> 03:23:00.900
and of course the owl

03:23:00.900 --> 03:23:02.020
is also you know

03:23:02.020 --> 03:23:03.020
symbolic for wisdom

03:23:03.020 --> 03:23:03.460
mm-hmm

03:23:03.460 --> 03:23:03.760
right

03:23:03.760 --> 03:23:04.980
um

03:23:04.980 --> 03:23:06.960
but also misfortune

03:23:06.960 --> 03:23:07.500
mm-hmm

03:23:07.500 --> 03:23:08.660
the

03:23:08.660 --> 03:23:09.700
you know

03:23:09.700 --> 03:23:10.600
the expression

03:23:10.600 --> 03:23:11.400
heads or tails

03:23:11.400 --> 03:23:13.740
comes from Greek coins

03:23:13.740 --> 03:23:15.000
that had an owl

03:23:15.000 --> 03:23:15.960
on the tail of them

03:23:15.960 --> 03:23:17.080
they had Athena's face

03:23:17.080 --> 03:23:17.820
on the front of them

03:23:17.820 --> 03:23:18.980
and they had the owl

03:23:18.980 --> 03:23:19.860
on the back side of them

03:23:19.860 --> 03:23:20.580
because the owl was

03:23:20.580 --> 03:23:22.020
Athena's creature

03:23:22.020 --> 03:23:22.500
hmm

03:23:22.500 --> 03:23:24.220
and uh

03:23:24.220 --> 03:23:25.020
so tails was

03:23:25.020 --> 03:23:25.280
you know

03:23:25.280 --> 03:23:25.840
the owl

03:23:25.840 --> 03:23:26.900
so it's like

03:23:26.900 --> 03:23:28.180
this ominous

03:23:28.180 --> 03:23:29.560
symbol

03:23:29.560 --> 03:23:30.100
mm-hmm

03:23:30.100 --> 03:23:31.120
and in Persian culture

03:23:31.120 --> 03:23:31.420
by the way

03:23:31.420 --> 03:23:31.860
same thing

03:23:31.860 --> 03:23:32.380
the greatest

03:23:32.380 --> 03:23:34.340
modern Persian novel

03:23:34.340 --> 03:23:35.780
the blind owl

03:23:35.780 --> 03:23:37.620
is a work of surrealism

03:23:37.620 --> 03:23:38.580
um

03:23:38.580 --> 03:23:40.000
and you know

03:23:40.000 --> 03:23:41.000
the central symbol

03:23:41.000 --> 03:23:41.640
is the owl

03:23:41.640 --> 03:23:42.100
mm-hmm

03:23:42.100 --> 03:23:42.900
it was written by a guy

03:23:42.900 --> 03:23:43.880
Sadek Hedayat

03:23:43.880 --> 03:23:45.100
who was the Persian

03:23:45.100 --> 03:23:45.940
translator of

03:23:45.940 --> 03:23:47.060
Franz Kafka's works

03:23:47.060 --> 03:23:50.160
and you see this

03:23:50.160 --> 03:23:50.940
all over Kafka

03:23:50.940 --> 03:23:51.520
particularly

03:23:51.520 --> 03:23:52.700
in the trial

03:23:52.700 --> 03:23:55.040
I wrote an essay

03:23:55.040 --> 03:23:55.780
um

03:23:55.780 --> 03:23:57.720
interpreting Kafka's trial

03:23:57.720 --> 03:23:58.060
uh

03:23:58.060 --> 03:23:59.000
that's in my anthology

03:23:59.000 --> 03:23:59.740
Lovers of Sofia

03:23:59.740 --> 03:24:01.060
where

03:24:01.060 --> 03:24:01.660
basically

03:24:01.660 --> 03:24:02.600
I make the case

03:24:02.600 --> 03:24:03.000
that

03:24:03.000 --> 03:24:03.800
Kafka

03:24:03.800 --> 03:24:04.880
is describing

03:24:04.880 --> 03:24:06.660
a spectral bureaucracy

03:24:06.660 --> 03:24:08.080
that Kafka

03:24:08.080 --> 03:24:08.600
knew

03:24:08.600 --> 03:24:09.000
and

03:24:09.000 --> 03:24:10.100
the key to this

03:24:10.100 --> 03:24:10.880
is you have to read

03:24:10.880 --> 03:24:12.200
his blue octavo notebooks

03:24:12.200 --> 03:24:13.120
he has these notebooks

03:24:13.120 --> 03:24:14.520
called the blue octavo notebooks

03:24:14.520 --> 03:24:16.060
when you set those

03:24:16.060 --> 03:24:17.340
next to the trial

03:24:17.340 --> 03:24:18.580
it acts as basically

03:24:18.580 --> 03:24:19.640
a key for understanding

03:24:19.640 --> 03:24:20.660
this kabbalistic text

03:24:20.660 --> 03:24:21.240
and you realize

03:24:21.240 --> 03:24:22.040
that Kafka knew

03:24:22.040 --> 03:24:23.640
to go back to

03:24:23.640 --> 03:24:25.420
luge farming

03:24:25.420 --> 03:24:27.220
that we're living

03:24:27.220 --> 03:24:28.440
inside some kind

03:24:28.440 --> 03:24:28.940
of a

03:24:28.940 --> 03:24:33.260
an oppressive

03:24:33.260 --> 03:24:35.440
convoluted

03:24:35.440 --> 03:24:36.300
uh

03:24:36.300 --> 03:24:37.040
shady

03:24:37.040 --> 03:24:37.940
scummy

03:24:37.940 --> 03:24:39.940
angelic bureaucracy

03:24:39.940 --> 03:24:41.640
it's like a spiritual

03:24:41.640 --> 03:24:42.620
control system

03:24:42.620 --> 03:24:44.460
and there's ways

03:24:44.460 --> 03:24:45.120
to beat it

03:24:45.120 --> 03:24:45.980
and like

03:24:45.980 --> 03:24:47.180
outsmart it

03:24:47.180 --> 03:24:47.960
and maneuver

03:24:47.960 --> 03:24:48.760
around it

03:24:48.760 --> 03:24:49.940
but it's very

03:24:49.940 --> 03:24:50.580
labyrinthine

03:24:50.580 --> 03:24:51.320
and very difficult

03:24:51.320 --> 03:24:52.340
what's the relationship

03:24:52.340 --> 03:24:53.500
between the devil

03:24:53.500 --> 03:24:54.820
and Prometheus

03:24:54.820 --> 03:24:55.380
the like

03:24:55.380 --> 03:24:56.060
rebel angels

03:24:56.060 --> 03:24:56.340
right

03:24:56.340 --> 03:24:57.640
so

03:24:57.640 --> 03:25:00.660
from a Judeo-Christian

03:25:00.660 --> 03:25:01.360
perspective

03:25:01.360 --> 03:25:05.060
the bringer

03:25:05.060 --> 03:25:05.900
of the light

03:25:05.900 --> 03:25:06.900
of technological

03:25:06.900 --> 03:25:07.580
science

03:25:07.580 --> 03:25:10.320
and

03:25:10.320 --> 03:25:11.340
a champion

03:25:11.340 --> 03:25:12.080
of humanity

03:25:12.080 --> 03:25:12.700
against

03:25:12.700 --> 03:25:13.680
a god father

03:25:13.680 --> 03:25:14.020
figure

03:25:14.020 --> 03:25:16.900
is going to

03:25:16.900 --> 03:25:17.720
inevitably be

03:25:17.720 --> 03:25:18.660
identified with

03:25:18.660 --> 03:25:19.020
Lucifer

03:25:19.020 --> 03:25:22.000
and in fact

03:25:22.000 --> 03:25:22.400
just on

03:25:22.400 --> 03:25:23.380
etymological terms

03:25:23.380 --> 03:25:23.860
alone

03:25:23.860 --> 03:25:24.820
Lucifer is a

03:25:24.820 --> 03:25:25.440
fairly decent

03:25:25.440 --> 03:25:26.320
Latin translation

03:25:26.320 --> 03:25:26.840
of the idea

03:25:26.840 --> 03:25:27.460
of Prometheus

03:25:27.460 --> 03:25:29.980
so

03:25:29.980 --> 03:25:30.920
if

03:25:30.920 --> 03:25:31.880
Zeus

03:25:31.880 --> 03:25:33.080
in the Greek

03:25:33.080 --> 03:25:33.640
pantheon

03:25:33.640 --> 03:25:34.220
or let's say

03:25:34.220 --> 03:25:34.860
Enlil

03:25:34.860 --> 03:25:35.720
in the Sumerian

03:25:35.720 --> 03:25:36.420
pantheon

03:25:36.420 --> 03:25:37.640
can be identified

03:25:37.640 --> 03:25:38.520
with Yahweh

03:25:38.520 --> 03:25:39.800
and

03:25:39.800 --> 03:25:40.760
according to

03:25:40.760 --> 03:25:41.140
Jesus

03:25:41.140 --> 03:25:42.280
in the canonical

03:25:42.280 --> 03:25:43.120
gospels

03:25:43.120 --> 03:25:44.040
he is the son

03:25:44.040 --> 03:25:44.580
of Yahweh

03:25:44.580 --> 03:25:45.500
and he's been

03:25:45.500 --> 03:25:46.380
sent by Yahweh

03:25:46.380 --> 03:25:47.680
well then

03:25:47.680 --> 03:25:48.220
Prometheus

03:25:48.220 --> 03:25:49.160
is the rebel

03:25:49.160 --> 03:25:50.360
against Yahweh

03:25:50.360 --> 03:25:51.580
meaning Prometheus

03:25:51.580 --> 03:25:52.140
is Satan

03:25:52.140 --> 03:25:53.640
okay

03:25:53.640 --> 03:25:55.180
now

03:25:56.320 --> 03:25:57.100
that's obviously

03:25:57.100 --> 03:25:57.820
a Judeo-Christian

03:25:57.820 --> 03:25:58.960
prism of interpretation

03:25:58.960 --> 03:26:00.040
and there would be

03:26:00.040 --> 03:26:00.960
an Islamic one too

03:26:00.960 --> 03:26:01.420
where you have

03:26:01.420 --> 03:26:01.620
you know

03:26:01.620 --> 03:26:02.440
the Islamic account

03:26:02.440 --> 03:26:03.280
of who Satan is

03:26:03.280 --> 03:26:04.000
which is also

03:26:04.000 --> 03:26:04.540
very interesting

03:26:04.540 --> 03:26:04.920
by the way

03:26:04.920 --> 03:26:05.180
because

03:26:05.180 --> 03:26:06.360
in the Islamic

03:26:06.360 --> 03:26:06.940
account

03:26:06.940 --> 03:26:09.780
Iblis

03:26:09.780 --> 03:26:10.600
or

03:26:10.600 --> 03:26:11.200
Shaytan

03:26:11.200 --> 03:26:13.040
is the leader

03:26:13.040 --> 03:26:14.040
of a group

03:26:14.040 --> 03:26:14.840
of beings

03:26:14.840 --> 03:26:15.980
who are called

03:26:15.980 --> 03:26:16.380
djinn

03:26:16.380 --> 03:26:18.800
and the djinn

03:26:18.800 --> 03:26:20.320
were humanoids

03:26:20.320 --> 03:26:21.780
made before man

03:26:21.780 --> 03:26:22.880
precede the

03:26:22.880 --> 03:26:23.760
Adamic race

03:26:23.760 --> 03:26:25.420
Adam

03:26:25.420 --> 03:26:26.140
is used

03:26:26.140 --> 03:26:26.620
in Arabic

03:26:26.620 --> 03:26:27.480
just like in Hebrew

03:26:27.480 --> 03:26:28.040
right

03:26:28.040 --> 03:26:29.240
and so

03:26:29.240 --> 03:26:30.840
the Adamic race

03:26:30.840 --> 03:26:31.580
is subsequent

03:26:31.580 --> 03:26:32.680
to an earlier race

03:26:32.680 --> 03:26:34.100
made not of clay

03:26:34.100 --> 03:26:35.020
but of fire

03:26:35.020 --> 03:26:36.840
beings made of fire

03:26:36.940 --> 03:26:37.540
again connection

03:26:37.540 --> 03:26:38.260
to Prometheus

03:26:38.260 --> 03:26:40.560
and according

03:26:40.560 --> 03:26:41.680
to the Islamic version

03:26:41.680 --> 03:26:43.300
Shaytan

03:26:43.300 --> 03:26:44.720
refused

03:26:44.720 --> 03:26:45.820
to bow

03:26:45.820 --> 03:26:46.960
before

03:26:46.960 --> 03:26:48.800
Allah's creation

03:26:48.800 --> 03:26:49.400
namely

03:26:49.400 --> 03:26:49.820
Adam

03:26:49.820 --> 03:26:51.260
because

03:26:51.260 --> 03:26:51.860
Adam

03:26:51.860 --> 03:26:53.460
from the perspective

03:26:53.460 --> 03:26:54.100
of the djinn

03:26:54.100 --> 03:26:54.720
was inferior

03:26:54.720 --> 03:26:55.260
to them

03:26:55.260 --> 03:26:56.260
and

03:26:56.260 --> 03:26:57.120
Iblis was like

03:26:57.120 --> 03:26:57.920
why should I bow

03:26:57.920 --> 03:26:59.440
to this inferior creation

03:26:59.440 --> 03:27:00.780
you just want me

03:27:00.780 --> 03:27:01.820
to bow to this thing

03:27:01.820 --> 03:27:03.240
because you're a tyrant

03:27:03.240 --> 03:27:04.740
and you want to

03:27:04.740 --> 03:27:05.560
lord over me

03:27:05.560 --> 03:27:06.660
and over all the angels

03:27:06.660 --> 03:27:07.560
and all the djinn

03:27:07.560 --> 03:27:09.140
and by

03:27:09.140 --> 03:27:10.320
by showing us

03:27:10.320 --> 03:27:10.980
that we have

03:27:10.980 --> 03:27:12.100
to be subservient

03:27:12.100 --> 03:27:12.580
to something

03:27:12.580 --> 03:27:13.020
that's actually

03:27:13.020 --> 03:27:13.840
inferior to us

03:27:13.840 --> 03:27:15.420
so out of pride

03:27:15.420 --> 03:27:17.140
Iblis doesn't bow

